2015;;A Dark Reflection;;British;;Tristan Loraine;;Georgina Sutcliffe, Rita Ramnani, Marina Sirtis, Stephen Tompkinson, Mark Dymond, Nicholas Day;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Dark_Reflection;;The film involves an air traffic controller who is suspended following a serious in-flight incident. When his journalist wife Helen Eastman (Georgina Sutcliffe) starts to ask questions, she uncovers a disturbing succession of cover-ups dating back to 1954.[7]